OOC: My God someone answered me?

::Whistler::
       "Oh is good old Iron Raptor still there.  After I tried to do 
something noble by protecting her, although I failed, and she left me for 
dead for months and BUILT A CITY AROUND MY BODY.  I'll be right there."  He 
walks slowly towards the coordinates.

--part1_ea.18bde24c.2890de8b_boundary
